'''2021年[[乌干达|烏干達]]大選'''於2021年1月14日（星期四）舉行，選舉新一屆[[烏干達國家元首|烏干達總統]]和[[乌干达议会|乌干达议会]]議員。本次選舉是時任總統[[约韦里·穆塞韦尼|约韦里·穆塞韦尼]]在1986年上台後第6次參選總統。<ref name=dw20210114>{{cite news |url=https://p.dw.com/p/3ntIn |title=Ugandans vote in contested presidential election |publisher=DW |date=2021-01-14}}</ref>最終约韦里·穆塞韦尼勝選，不過反對派宣稱選舉舞弊，呼籲選民抵制結果<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/sudan-president-won-election-20210116/5740382.html |title=乌干达现任总统胜选 |accessdate=2021-01-17 |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122005041/https://www.voachinese.com/a/sudan-president-won-election-20210116/5740382.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==選舉制度==
總統選舉採取[[两轮选举制|两轮选举制]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Presidential Electons Act 2000 | Uganda Legal Information Institute|url=https://ulii.org/ug/legislation/consolidated-act/142|access-date=2020-09-18|website=ulii.org|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115162005/https://ulii.org/ug/legislation/consolidated-act/142|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年12月，[[乌干达议会|乌干达议会]]通過修改憲法，取消總統候選人年齡上限為75歲的限制。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.voanews.com/a/uganda-parliament-law-yoweri-museveni-re-election/4172340.html |title=Ugandan MPs Clear Way for Museveni to Seek Re-election |publisher=VOA |date=2017-12-20 |accessdate=2021-01-17 |archive-date=2017-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171228073610/https://www.voanews.com/a/uganda-parliament-law-yoweri-museveni-re-election/4172340.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

新一屆烏干達議會有529個席位，353席由單議席選區選出，以[[領先者當選|領先者當選]]，另外146席只限女性參選，1區1席，30席由特別選舉團選出，其中軍方佔10席，青年佔5席，老人佔5席，工會佔5席，殘疾人士佔5席。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ilo.org/dyn/natlex/docs/ELECTRONIC/44038/90491/F206329993/UGA44038.pdf|title=Constitution|accessdate=2021-01-17|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918153033/https://www.ilo.org/dyn/natlex/docs/ELECTRONIC/44038/90491/F206329993/UGA44038.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ec.or.ug/sites/default/files/press/VET%20Handbook%202020.pdf |title=Electoral handbook |accessdate=2021-01-17 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129045142/https://www.ec.or.ug/sites/default/files/press/VET%20Handbook%202020.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/3613/#_ftn1|title=IFES Election Guide | Elections: Uganda National Assembly 2021|website=www.electionguide.org|accessdate=2021-01-17|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122193008/https://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/3613/#_ftn1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==選舉結果==
2021年1月16日，選舉委員會主席西蒙·比亚巴卡马（Simon Mugenyi Byabakama）宣佈穆塞韋尼在總統選舉勝出。<ref name="BBCResults">{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-55689665 |website=BBC |title=Uganda: Veteran leader Yoweri Museveni declared election winner |date=2021-01-16 |accessdate=2021-01-17 |archive-date=2021-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121231701/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-55689665 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在選舉結果公佈前，反對派總統候選人[[波比·懷恩|波比·懷恩]]對記者表示這次是「烏干達歷史上最欺詐的選舉」，又表示自己在首都[[坎帕拉|坎帕拉]]的住所被軍方士兵包圍，他在試圖外出時被士兵阻止，他們說這是上級命令。<ref name="dw20210116">{{cite news |url=https://p.dw.com/p/3o0s9 |title=Uganda: Yoweri Museveni declared winner amid election fraud allegations |publisher=DW |date=2021-01-16}}</ref><ref name="GraunResults"/>穆塞韋尼在1月16日晚的全國講話上否認選舉舞弊指控，宣稱這次「可能是1962年以來最沒有作弊的選舉」。<ref name="BBCResults"/><ref name="GraunResults">{{cite news |work=The Guardian |title=Museveni declared election winner in Uganda as rival Bobi Wine alleges fraud |first1=Emmanuel |last1=Akinwotu |first2=Samuel |last2=Okiror |date=2021-01-16 |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/16/uganda-president-wins-decisive-election-as-bobi-wine-alleges |accessdate=2021-01-17 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123191647/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/jan/16/uganda-president-wins-decisive-election-as-bobi-wine-alleges |dead-url=no }}</ref>比亚巴卡马要求波比·懷恩公開他宣稱的選舉舞弊的證據。<ref name="BBCResults"/>

